----------------------------------------------------
Buildwords Script

#!/bin/bash

sed '1,27d' |

sed '/<\/tr>/d' |

sed '731,747d' |

tr -d '[:blank:]' |

sed '/<tr>/d' |

sed '/<br>/d' |

sed 's/<[^>]*>//g' |

sed '/^$/d' |  

sed '1~2d' |

tr [:upper:] [:lower:] |

sed s/\`/\'/g |

sed 's/\,/\n/g' |
 
tr -c '[^pk'mnwlhaeiou]' '?'
-----------------------------------------------------

Check the misspelled Hawaiian words:

$ cat assign2.html | tr -cs "pk'mnwlhaeiou" '[\n*]' | 
tr '[:upper:]' '[:lower:]'| sort -u | comm -23 - hwords > misHawaiian

$ wc -w misHawaiian
Output:
204 misHawaiian

Thus, there are 204 misspelling of Hawaiian words.

Check the misspelled English words:

$ cat assign2.html | tr -cs 'A-Za-z' '[\n*]' | 
tr '[:upper:]' '[:lower:]' | sort -u | comm -23 - words > misEnglish

$ wc -w misEnglish
Output:
38 misEnglish

Thus, there are 38 misspelling of Hawaiian.
